description: Elevation Gold Mining Corporation acquires, explores for, develops, and operates precious metal properties in the United States. The company explores for gold and silver deposits. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Moss Gold-Silver mine located in Mohave County, Arizona. The company was formerly known as Northern Vertex Mining Corp. and changed its name to Elevation Gold Mining Corporation in September 2021. Elevation Gold Mining Corporation was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Tim J. Swendseid CFA, MBA, P.E.
